WEBVTT

00:01.058 --> 00:02.037
There are two kinds of folks

00:02.064 --> 00:03.664
who sit around thinking
about how to kill people:

00:03.998 --> 00:05.724
psychopaths
and mystery writers.

00:06.062 --> 00:07.084
I'm the kind that pays better.

00:07.185 --> 00:07.885
Who am I?

00:07.974 --> 00:09.113
I'm Rick Castle.

00:09.114 --> 00:09.514
Castle.

00:09.548 --> 00:10.208
Castle.

00:10.209 --> 00:12.209
I really am ruggedly handsome,
aren't I?

00:12.455 --> 00:14.645
Every writer needs  inspiration.
And I found mine.

00:14.755 --> 00:15.574
Detective Kate Beckett.

00:15.609 --> 00:16.629
- Beckett.
- Beckett.

00:16.664 --> 00:18.570
- Nikki Heat?
- The character he's basing on you.

00:18.616 --> 00:20.102
And thanks to my friendship
with the mayor,

00:20.103 --> 00:21.103
I get to be on her case.

00:21.137 --> 00:23.080
I would be happy
to let you spank me.

00:23.115 --> 00:23.991
And together, we catch killers

00:24.939 --> 00:25.927
We make a pretty
good team, you know?

00:26.028 --> 00:27.028
Like Starsky and Hutch.

00:27.162 --> 00:27.856
Turner and Hooch.

00:27.957 --> 00:29.557
You do remind me
a little of Hooch.

